
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
	<main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 mt-20 text-black">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p><em>Last updated: 26 January 2026</em></p>
		<p>Victoria IT ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs) contained in the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>1.</b> <span class="italic">Collection of Personal Information</span></h2>
		<p>We may collect personal information such as your <b>name</b>, <b>email address</b>, <b>phone number</b>, and any other information you voluntarily provide to us through forms, contact requests, or other interactions with our website.</p>
		<p>We may also automatically collect certain information about your device and usage of our website through cookies and analytics tools (such as Amplitude), including:</p>
		<ul class="list-disc ml-6">
			<li><b>IP address</b></li>
			<li><b>Browser type</b></li>
			<li><b>Pages visited</b></li>
			<li><b>Time and date of visit</b></li>
			<li><b>Referring website</b></li>
		</ul>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>2.</b> <span class="italic">Use of Personal Information</span></h2>
		<p>We use your personal information to:</p>
		<ul class="list-disc ml-6">
			<li><b>Provide and improve our services</b></li>
			<li><b>Respond to your enquiries and requests</b></li>
			<li><b>Analyse website usage and improve user experience</b></li>
			<li><b>Comply with legal obligations</b></li>
		</ul>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>3.</b> <span class="italic">Disclosure of Personal Information</span></h2>
		<p>We may disclose your personal information to:</p>
		<ul class="list-disc ml-6">
			<li><b>Service providers and partners</b> who assist us in operating our website and providing our services (e.g., analytics providers such as Amplitude)</li>
			<li><b>Government authorities or law enforcement</b> as required by law</li>
		</ul>
		<p><b>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</b></p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>4.</b> <span class="italic">Cookies and Analytics</span></h2>
		<p>Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to collect information about your browsing activities. We use analytics tools (including Amplitude) to understand how visitors interact with our site. You can manage your cookie preferences at any time using our cookie consent banner.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>5.</b> <span class="italic">Overseas Disclosure</span></h2>
		<p>Some of our service providers (including analytics providers) may store or process your personal information overseas. We take reasonable steps to ensure that any overseas recipients comply with Australian privacy laws.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>6.</b> <span class="italic">Data Security</span></h2>
		<p>We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from misuse, interference, loss, unauthorised access, modification, or disclosure.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>7.</b> <span class="italic">Access and Correction</span></h2>
		<p>You may request access to or correction of your personal information by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@victoriait.com.au"><b>info@victoriait.com.au</b></a>.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>8.</b> <span class="italic">Complaints</span></h2>
		<p>If you have a complaint about how we handle your personal information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@victoriait.com.au"><b>info@victoriait.com.au</b></a>. We will respond to your complaint as soon as possible.</p>
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2"><b>9.</b> <span class="italic">Changes to This Policy</span></h2>
		<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on our website.</p>
		<hr />
	</main>
</Layout>
